        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/DEGREE_PLATO>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/DEGREE_TWADDELL>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/FemtoGM-PER-L>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/GM-PER-CentiM3>,
