        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/FUR_Long>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/FemtoM>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/GAUGE_FR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/HectoM>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/IN>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloM>,
