        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MegaJ>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MegaTOE>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MegaV-A-HR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MegaV-A_Reactive-HR>,
