        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/DeciB_M> ;
    ns1:latexDefinition "\\(L_W = 10 \\log_{10} \\frac{P}{P_0} dB\\), where \\(P\\) is sound power and the reference value is \\(P_0 =1pW\\)."^^ns1:LatexString .

