        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloSEC>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloYR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MIN>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MIN_Sidereal>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MO>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MO_MeanGREGORIAN>,
